DEVICE FUNCTIONALITY:

Screen displays device name, battery percentage, sensor data, messages sent/recieved

Battery percentage monitored

Connects to phone over wifi to program device name

Communicates to other device over LoRa

Collects sensor data at regular intervals

2 buttons, each sends a different message

Device is in recieve mode until button pressed to send




CODE ORGANIZATION:

Each sensor/battery/screen/chip has its own 'library' file where all its functions are written

Executable code is written in the 'main' file

Refer to schematic for pinouts
